eaten it before.

145
00:16:33,990 --> 00:16:39,130
♪Cherish you deep within♪

146
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:43,100
♪A flower of affection♪

147
00:16:43,180 --> 00:16:48,340
♪Blooms without fading, forever in love♪

148
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:52,000
♪Fold a kite♪

149
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:57,280
♪Let it fly with the wind
into sweet dreams♪

150
00:16:58,580 --> 00:17:00,900
♪The beautiful moments we shared♪

151
00:17:00,980 --> 00:17:06,180
♪Last through time,
we never leave each other♪

152
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:10,720
♪My love sees♪

153
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:13,000
♪The sun rising and the moon setting♪

154
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:17,200
♪Your face stays vivid in my mind♪

155
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:19,680
♪Two hearts♪

156
00:17:19,740 --> 00:17:21,960
