you're still not thinking straight.

162
00:17:38,536 --> 00:17:39,670
It just feels as though

163
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:42,120
I've been together with you

164
00:17:42,710 --> 00:17:44,390
for a long time.

165
00:17:48,410 --> 00:17:49,650
From now on, you'll stay with me.

166
00:17:49,860 --> 00:17:51,380
Whatever I eat, you'll eat too.

167
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:55,050
♪Two hearts♪

168
00:17:55,090 --> 00:17:57,330
♪Bound to each other♪

169
00:17:57,370 --> 00:18:01,550
♪Like flowing water,
love and hate continue♪

170
00:18:01,650 --> 00:18:03,890
♪I only wish♪

171
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:06,170
♪For your unwavering heart♪

172
00:18:06,210 --> 00:18:10,390
♪You are still there when I turn back♪

173
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:12,730
♪As passionate as we first met♪

174
00:18:12,770 --> 00:18:15,010
♪I hold your hands through eternity♪

175
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:19,210
♪Time cannot separate us♪

176
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:23,210
♪Our longings go on♪

177
00:18:46,950 --> 00:18:47,860
He's arrived.

178
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:50,970
Yes.

179
00:18:52,224 --> 00:18:53,250
Rest assured.

180
00:18:53,592 --> 00:18:55,300
I will never let him hurt you again.

181
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:58,100
What about you?

182
00:19:00,390 --> 00:19:01,750
I will end this.

183
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:03,890
Sanlang.

184
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:05,950
Ci.

185
00:19:06,776 --> 00:19:07,376
Shaojun.

186
00:19:09,304 --> 00:19:10,660
How are your injuries, Sanlang?

187
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:12,730
Nothing too serious.

188
00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:14,280
You two have a chat.

189
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,800
I'll go prepare some food.

190
00:19:25,490 --> 00:19:26,750
Do you know

191
00:19:27,280 --> 00:19:28,100
His Majesty is coming?

192
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:31,210
Yes.

193
00:19:31,430 --> 00:19:32,390
You captured Gao Xiu,

194
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:33,650
forced a peace treaty

195
00:19:33,736 --> 00:19:35,288
and won the respect of the three armies.

196
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:36,936
His Majesty has always been wary of you.

197
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:38,490
Now, I fear

198
00:19:38,670 --> 00:19:40,040
it will only get worse.

199
00:19:41,384 --> 00:19:43,450
The tree desires calm,
but the wind won't stop.

200
00:19:44,450 --> 00:19:46,100
He's long had the intent to kill me.

201
00:19:46,470 --> 00:19:47,800
Whatever I do,

202
00:19:48,024 --> 00:19:49,480
there's no turning back now.

203
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:51,140
Rather than live in fear,

204
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,620
I will face him head-on.

205
00:19:52,856 --> 00:19:54,280
That's my only hope of survival.

206
00:19:56,848 --> 00:19:57,990
What is your plan, Sanlang?

207
00:19:59,730 --> 00:20:01,620
I intend to reveal the truth

208
00:20:01,856 --> 00:20:03,360
about Prince Qi's case

209
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,664
in front of the three armies,

210
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,650
to redress justice for my father

211
00:20:06,650 --> 00:20:07,650
and Yueluo.

212
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:10,380
This is a death wish.

213
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:13,170
At this point,

214
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:15,300
it's the only thing I can do

215
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:16,670
for my father and Yueluo.

216
00:20:17,064 --> 00:20:18,470
What crime has Yueluo committed?

217
00:20:18,488 --> 00:20:19,990
Who else but me can bear this burden?

218
00:20:20,968 --> 00:20:22,750
Just pretend you know nothing

219
00:20:22,984 --> 00:20:24,240
lest you get implicated.

220
00:20:24,328 --> 00:20:25,704
What crime has Yueluo committed?

221
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:27,250
I will respond to your call

222
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:28,430
on behalf of the world.

223
00:20:28,696 --> 00:20:29,950
What harm is there in that?

224
00:20:32,930 --> 00:20:34,190
I have been taught since childhood

225
00:20:34,450 --> 00:20:35,930
to fight for my family's interests.

226
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:37,380
In the end,

227
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:38,488
family ties were severed,

228
00:20:38,488 --> 00:20:39,520
close friends were harmed

229
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:40,856
and I was estranged from my loved ones.

230
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:42,380
Apart from fighting,

231
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,620
I know nothing else.

232
00:20:46,650 --> 00:20:48,380
Are you going to keep fighting?

233
00:20:48,450 --> 00:20:49,230
Of course.

234
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,710
In this world,

235
00:20:50,710 --> 00:20:51,690
whether good or bad,

236
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,300
nothing comes without a price.

237
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,470
To punish evil, we must fight.

238
00:20:55,576 --> 00:20:57,336
To uphold justice, we must
fight even more.

239
00:20:57,650 --> 00:20:58,450
This time,

240
00:20:58,856 --> 00:21:00,120
it's a fight for the people,

241
00:21:00,120 --> 00:21:01,560
for justice and righteousness.

242
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:07,750
I am willing to stand by your side

243
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:09,520
and fight

244
00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:11,410
to restore justice for Yueluo.

245
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:19,140
Shaojun, I am grateful

246
00:21:19,390 --> 00:21:21,450
for your righteousness.

247
00:21:29,450 --> 00:21:30,040
Sanlang,

248
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:32,840
only today have I realized

249
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,560
that you and I are not opponents.

250
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,150
We are confidants

251
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:39,040
and friends.

252
00:21:58,690 --> 00:22:00,100
Why are the streets of Yueluo

253
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,730
filled only with
the elderly and children?

254
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,280
Every year, Yueluo offers
slaves as tribute.

255
00:22:05,390 --> 00:22:07,470
The young men and women
are sent to Liang.

256
00:22:10,190 --> 00:22:11,230
Look at their faces.

257
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,280
They didn't want to be slaves,

258
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:14,860
so they scarred their own faces

259
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:16,410
and covered them with tattoos.

260
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:17,860
It is to encourage themselves

261
00:22:18,020 --> 00:22:19,360
to face life with courage.

262
00:22:22,190 --> 00:22:23,750
Back in Liang,

263
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:26,140
we were used to slavery
as a form of tribute.

264
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,470
But Yueluo

265
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:30,230
has seen 20 years of broken families

266
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:32,250
and unbearable pain.

267
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:37,170
I never knew these things.

268
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:39,930
Your Highness,

269
00:22:40,088 --> 00:22:41,650
Yueluo is a territory
of the Liang state,

270
00:22:41,650 --> 00:22:43,190
and its people are also your subjects.

271
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:45,230
All they want is to live

272
00:22:45,230 --> 00:22:46,690
like ordinary citizens,

273
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:47,470
to live in peace

274
00:22:48,020 --> 00:22:49,280
and safety.

275
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:54,410
I know that you are
kind-hearted and benevolent,

276
00:22:54,456 --> 00:22:56,008
but forgive me for speaking bluntly,

277
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:58,340
if you wish to become a wise ruler,

278
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:00,710
benevolence alone is not enough.

279
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:02,100
You must also

280
00:23:02,232 --> 00:23:03,864
have the boldness
to surpass the Emperor.

281
00:23:04,150 --> 00:23:05,040
Shaojun,

282
00:23:05,620 --> 00:23:06,670
don't speak recklessly.

