00:23:07,816 --> 00:23:09,750
Do you truly not understand

284
00:23:10,312 --> 00:23:12,060
what Princess Yong'an's trial
was all about?

285
00:23:12,970 --> 00:23:15,190
If you only follow the Emperor's orders,

286
00:23:15,690 --> 00:23:16,990
when will you ever become

287
00:23:16,990 --> 00:23:19,560
a ruler who can stand on your own?

288
00:23:20,952 --> 00:23:23,016
I'm torn between filial piety
and righteousness.

289
00:23:24,256 --> 00:23:25,890
But he is my father.

290
00:23:26,992 --> 00:23:28,380
What choice do I have?

291
00:23:28,450 --> 00:23:30,470
What is it that you truly
want to uphold?

292
00:23:30,528 --> 00:23:31,860
Loyalty to your father,

293
00:23:32,140 --> 00:23:33,690
or righteousness for the people?

294
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:48,700
(Palace, Yueluo)

295
00:23:49,650 --> 00:23:50,450
Father.

296
00:23:51,060 --> 00:23:51,910
What is it?

297
00:23:52,910 --> 00:23:53,970
If I may be so bold,

298
00:23:54,430 --> 00:23:55,390
Father,

299
00:23:55,910 --> 00:23:57,470
please restore justice for Yueluo.

300
00:23:58,040 --> 00:23:58,860
Justice?

301
00:23:59,930 --> 00:24:00,710
Back then,

302
00:24:00,990 --> 00:24:02,910
the former lord of Yueluo, Xiao Haitian,

303
00:24:02,936 --> 00:24:04,940
was accused of plotting
against my uncle, Prince Qi.

304
00:24:04,950 --> 00:24:06,710
But there were no witnesses or evidence,

305
00:24:06,910 --> 00:24:08,280
and many details were questionable.

306
00:24:08,650 --> 00:24:10,690
If the people of Yueluo are
implicated again,

307
00:24:10,952 --> 00:24:12,450
it would be an affront to humanity

308
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:14,170
and a travesty of justice.

309
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:15,880
Are you saying

310
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:17,560
that I wronged them?

311
00:24:17,928 --> 00:24:19,890
You have always been a diligent
and kind ruler,

312
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:21,560
but I believe

313
00:24:21,710 --> 00:24:23,060
that you may have been deceived

314
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:24,520
and passed a wrong judgment.

315
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:26,450
You are the ruler of the nation

316
00:24:26,890 --> 00:24:28,340
and Yueluo's sovereign.

317
00:24:28,936 --> 00:24:31,100
You should restore justice
to the people of Yueluo.

318
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,490
Who has been filling
your head with gossip?

319
00:24:34,568 --> 00:24:37,256
You've taught me benevolence,
righteousness, propriety, and wisdom.

320
00:24:37,528 --> 00:24:39,410
I know what is right and wrong.

321
00:24:39,432 --> 00:24:41,280
I know we should rule the world
with benevolence,

322
00:24:41,448 --> 00:24:42,650
govern the world with virtue,

323
00:24:42,650 --> 00:24:43,890
secure the world with propriety,

324
00:24:44,140 --> 00:24:45,380
and put the people first.

325
00:24:46,048 --> 00:24:47,450
My beliefs

326
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,520
and my actions

327
00:24:48,890 --> 00:24:50,210
are not influenced by anyone else.

328
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:52,020
It all comes from my own heart.

329
00:24:52,632 --> 00:24:53,360
I will not

330
00:24:54,096 --> 00:24:55,020
waver.

331
00:24:56,224 --> 00:24:57,560
So, in your view,

332
00:24:58,696 --> 00:25:00,230
what should I do?

333
00:25:01,248 --> 00:25:02,800
I would like to organize a ceremony

334
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:04,620
to reward the three armies
on your behalf,

335
00:25:05,140 --> 00:25:07,450
and to reward the soldiers of Yueluo,

336
00:25:08,048 --> 00:25:09,470
thus restoring justice to Yueluo.

337
00:25:10,170 --> 00:25:12,910
The three armies and all the people
will surely remember you

338
00:25:13,020 --> 00:25:14,230
as a great and kind ruler.

339
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,730
If you say so,

340
00:25:21,190 --> 00:25:22,040
you may proceed.

341
00:25:22,930 --> 00:25:23,800
Father,

342
00:25:24,230 --> 00:25:25,080
thank you.

343
00:25:46,690 --> 00:25:47,360
Greetings,

344
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:48,450
Your Majesty.

345
00:25:49,450 --> 00:25:52,340
You are indeed
a pillar of the nation, Sanlang.

346
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:56,040
Your reputation now echoes
throughout the three armies.

347
00:25:56,650 --> 00:25:57,470
I

348
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:59,360
am unsure

349
00:25:59,450 --> 00:26:01,170
how to reward you.

350
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:03,540
The defeat of the Wei army

351
00:26:03,650 --> 00:26:04,620
was not my doing.

352
00:26:05,016 --> 00:26:06,170
If anyone is to be rewarded,

353
00:26:06,520 --> 00:26:09,040
it's the soldiers and people of Yueluo.

354
00:26:11,410 --> 00:26:13,424
I have already ordered
the Crown Prince to organize

355
00:26:13,424 --> 00:26:14,670
a grand ceremony in three days

356
00:26:14,670 --> 00:26:15,840
to reward the three armies.

357
00:26:18,664 --> 00:26:19,750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

358
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:25,250
Besides the soldiers who fought bravely,

359
00:26:25,860 --> 00:26:29,430
I've also heard about a physician
with miraculous healing skills.

360
00:26:29,670 --> 00:26:31,780
I should reward her as well.

361
00:26:33,592 --> 00:26:35,710
The army's physicians
are all skilled and kind.

362
00:26:36,280 --> 00:26:39,340
I thank you on their behalf.

363
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:42,950
You seem to be hiding someone.

364
00:26:44,288 --> 00:26:46,620
There's no one in the army
that would be of interest to you.

365
00:26:46,690 --> 00:26:48,380
I have nothing to hide.

366
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,750
If that's the case,

367
00:26:52,910 --> 00:26:54,696
then we will decide the rewards
and punishments

368
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:57,410
on the day of the grand ceremony.

369
00:27:14,950 --> 00:27:15,690
Your Majesty.

370
00:27:15,990 --> 00:27:17,140
Everything is ready.

371
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:21,890
Sanlang is no longer the boy
he once was.

372
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:25,410
It all began with Yueluo,

373
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:29,060
so it shall end with Yueluo.

374
00:27:43,230 --> 00:27:44,300
You're back.

375
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:46,620
Why aren't you asleep yet?

376
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:48,470
All thanks to you

377
00:27:48,470 --> 00:27:49,880
for coming back so late.

378
00:27:54,100 --> 00:27:54,600
Come.

379
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,250
Sit here,

380
00:28:01,250 --> 00:28:02,344
I'll help you dry the clothes.

381
00:28:20,020 --> 00:28:20,840
There, it's done.

382
00:28:22,152 --> 00:28:23,450
Now it's your turn to push me.

383
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:25,020
Last time, I let you off easy.

384
00:28:48,150 --> 00:28:49,840
When all this is over,

385
00:28:50,150 --> 00:28:51,840
I'll build a small house,

386
00:28:52,470 --> 00:28:54,250
and move this swing there.

387
00:28:54,930 --> 00:28:56,640
That way, no matter how far we go,

388
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:59,020
we'll always have a place to call home.

389
00:29:02,390 --> 00:29:04,060
This swing is clearly mine,

390
00:29:04,250 --> 00:29:05,910
