391
00:29:07,450 --> 00:29:09,020
Who said this swing is yours?

392
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:14,420
(Ci, Xia)

393
00:29:15,712 --> 00:29:16,620
Sit down.

394
00:29:21,816 --> 00:29:23,840
You're always mooching food and drinks,

395
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:25,230
