396
00:29:27,856 --> 00:29:28,776
Now that I'm no longer

397
00:29:28,832 --> 00:29:30,360
a commander,

398
00:29:30,832 --> 00:29:31,730
I'm afraid

399
00:29:32,088 --> 00:29:33,970
