to pay rent anymore.

400
00:29:35,336 --> 00:29:36,640
Then work

401
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:38,080
for me.

402
00:29:38,430 --> 00:29:41,080
If you do your chores well enough,

403
00:29:41,210 --> 00:29:43,730
I might just take you in.

404
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:46,780
You're giving me all the work,

405
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:48,040
what about you?

406
00:29:48,250 --> 00:29:49,100
Me?

407
00:29:49,328 --> 00:29:50,970
I'll sit here on the swing
and supervise.

408
00:29:55,730 --> 00:29:56,540
Fine.

409
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:57,670
If you say so.

410
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:12,060
Tomorrow is the reward ceremony.

411
00:30:13,064 --> 00:30:14,560
I've asked Yifei to guard this place.

412
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,380
As long as you stay hidden,

413
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:17,580
you'll be fine.

414
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:19,380
What about you?

415
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:21,100
Me?

416
00:30:21,490 --> 00:30:24,280
Of course, I'll go receive
my rewards and honors.

417
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:30,140
Once the ceremony is over tomorrow,

418
00:30:30,410 --> 00:30:32,410
you'd better come straight home.

419
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:37,380
Your pinching skill is improving
day by day.

420
00:30:37,890 --> 00:30:39,410
Whoever ends up marrying you

421
00:30:39,820 --> 00:30:40,880
would be one unlucky man.

422
00:30:41,990 --> 00:30:44,320
But compared to how you
hurt me back then,

423
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:45,710
it's nothing.

424
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,860
Wouldn't you agree?

425
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,250
If only this night

426
00:31:06,890 --> 00:31:08,840
could last a little longer.

427
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:13,410
I've already given you the swing,

428
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:16,580
why are you still unhappy?

429
00:31:19,340 --> 00:31:20,950
I don't want the swing.

430
00:31:21,340 --> 00:31:22,820
I want you.

431
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:42,320
Come back soon.

432
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:20,800
Wait for my return.

433
00:33:05,130 --> 00:33:12,930
(Happiness)

434
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,410
(I've never feared death.)

435
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:21,710
(But since I met you,)

436
00:33:22,456 --> 00:33:23,490
(I realized that this world)

437
00:33:23,490 --> 00:33:24,890
(isn't all darkness and pain.)

438
00:33:25,650 --> 00:33:27,620
(There are many things
worth cherishing.)

439
00:33:28,280 --> 00:33:29,520
(So I began)

440
00:33:30,250 --> 00:33:32,080
(to long for more.)

441
00:33:32,390 --> 00:33:33,520
(In order to save me,)

442
00:33:34,410 --> 00:33:35,780
(you pretended to be my wife.)

443
00:33:36,340 --> 00:33:38,300
(To you, it was a temporary measure,)

444
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:41,340
(but to me, it was a lifelong promise.)

445
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:44,230
(You're the only one for me, Jiang Ci.)

446
00:33:46,100 --> 00:33:47,120
(The future is uncertain.)

447
00:33:48,410 --> 00:33:49,520
(So I'm sealing)

448
00:33:50,650 --> 00:33:52,360
(our marriage right now.)

449
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:55,860
(First bow to the heavens.)

450
00:33:58,050 --> 00:34:01,570
♪Fortunate to walk together,
even for a moment♪

451
00:34:01,730 --> 00:34:03,520
(Second bow to the earth.)

452
00:34:04,930 --> 00:34:09,330
♪Who could have known
how we'd arrive at today♪

453
00:34:09,450 --> 00:34:13,730
♪A wilted heart with no one
to depend on♪

454
00:34:13,850 --> 00:34:17,350
♪Is the reason I cannot bear to part♪

455
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:24,210
♪Our last burning memory in my heart♪

