457
00:34:29,210 --> 00:34:32,990
♪No more memories of you♪

458
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:37,510
♪A wilted heart with no one
to depend on♪

459
00:34:37,630 --> 00:34:41,130
♪Is the reason I cannot bear to part♪

460
00:34:41,850 --> 00:34:47,990
♪Our last burning memory in my heart♪

461
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:52,870
♪From then on, no more pain or regret♪

462
00:34:52,990 --> 00:34:56,790
♪No more memories of you♪

463
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:00,540
Yifei,

464
00:35:00,850 --> 00:35:02,100
guard this place with your life.

465
00:35:03,370 --> 00:35:04,270
I will.

466
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,250
As for Jiang Ci,

467
00:35:07,250 --> 00:35:08,640
I'll leave her in your care, Ziming.

468
00:35:09,690 --> 00:35:11,000
His Majesty will definitely move in

469
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,250
on Jiang Ci during the ceremony.

470
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:14,100
She must not be discovered.

471
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:16,540
Rest assured,

472
00:35:16,790 --> 00:35:18,670
I will protect Ci with my life.

473
00:35:19,810 --> 00:35:20,790
Today's ceremony

474
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,330
could be a trap.

475
00:35:22,730 --> 00:35:24,290
Besides, you have no evidence.

476
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:25,830
At this point,

477
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:27,900
there is no other way.

478
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:29,730
Since I've taken this route,

479
00:35:29,900 --> 00:35:30,810
I won't turn back.

480
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:33,750
What's this?

481
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:36,310
