482
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,020
Without you,

483
00:35:40,170 --> 00:35:41,140
no plan would be complete.

484
00:35:55,040 --> 00:35:55,850
Shaojun,

485
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,270
let's go.

486
00:36:12,900 --> 00:36:14,120
Take your men

487
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:15,940
and find Princess Yong'an.

488
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:18,150
Today's a grand occasion.

489
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:20,790
It'd be a shame if they missed it.

490
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:22,710
Yes.

491
00:36:26,870 --> 00:36:29,710
We welcome Your Majesty.

492
00:36:58,650 --> 00:37:00,000
Everyone, rise.

493
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,580
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

494
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:08,020
You, the soldiers of the three armies,

495
00:37:08,170 --> 00:37:10,350
have defended our great state

496
00:37:10,350 --> 00:37:11,640
and repelled the foreign invaders.

497
00:37:11,650 --> 00:37:12,810
You deserve praise and merit.

498
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,080
I

499
00:37:15,250 --> 00:37:17,020
have brought fine liquor and meat

500
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,690
to reward you all.

501
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:22,100
When you return to Liang,

502
00:37:22,730 --> 00:37:23,790
I will personally

503
00:37:24,270 --> 00:37:25,650
grant you titles and rewards.

504
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:28,640
- Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.
- Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

505
00:37:29,770 --> 00:37:30,730
Father,

506
00:37:31,496 --> 00:37:33,650
the soldiers of Yueluo fought valiantly
against the Wei.

507
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:36,040
Please grant them the same rewards

508
00:37:36,370 --> 00:37:38,290
so that they may be consoled.

509
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:42,230
Anyone who has contributed
to our nation,

510
00:37:42,730 --> 00:37:45,370
regardless of any past crimes,

511
00:37:45,850 --> 00:37:46,940
will be

512
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:48,330
treated equally

513
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:50,210
and rewarded accordingly.

514
00:37:58,480 --> 00:37:59,750
People of Yueluo,

515
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:01,520
do you have anything to say?

516
00:38:04,984 --> 00:38:07,096
We, the people of Yueluo,
humbly accept the decree.

517
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:09,710
Your Majesty,

518
00:38:09,770 --> 00:38:10,870
I have something to say.

519
00:38:36,850 --> 00:38:37,650
Wei Zhao,

520
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:40,190
what do you wish to say?

521
00:38:41,730 --> 00:38:43,000
I wish to speak about

522
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:45,000
Prince Qi's case from 20 years ago.

523
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,980
Prince Qi's old case?

524
00:38:49,690 --> 00:38:50,520
What is there to say?

525
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,040
The injustice in Yueluo

526
00:38:52,330 --> 00:38:53,560
must be addressed today.

527
00:38:54,640 --> 00:38:56,170
- The injustice in Yueluo
- The injustice in Yueluo

528
00:38:56,370 --> 00:38:58,210
- must be addressed today.
