531
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:05,400
He was not the actual murderer
of Prince Qi.

532
00:39:06,370 --> 00:39:07,750
If it wasn't Xiao Haitian,

533
00:39:08,770 --> 00:39:09,870
then who was it?

534
00:39:11,770 --> 00:39:13,250
The true murderer of Prince Qi...

535
00:39:25,080 --> 00:39:26,790
Mother, why are you here?

536
00:39:26,830 --> 00:39:29,080
Didn't you ask us to come celebrate?

537
00:39:29,104 --> 00:39:29,980
Yes.

538
00:39:33,370 --> 00:39:34,920
Today's reward ceremony

539
00:39:35,608 --> 00:39:37,160
is meant for the people of Yueluo

540
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:39,080
to share in the victory.

541
00:39:43,330 --> 00:39:44,140
Wei Zhao,

542
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:45,960
step forward.

543
00:40:13,650 --> 00:40:14,440
Wei Zhao,

544
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:17,850
you just said Xiao Haitian was wronged,

545
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:20,350
and that Yueluo was wronged.

546
00:40:20,770 --> 00:40:22,870
Why don't you explain it

547
00:40:23,290 --> 00:40:24,580
in front of the people of Yueluo?

548
00:40:27,170 --> 00:40:27,870
Your Lordship,

549
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,770
what's happening?

550
00:40:28,936 --> 00:40:31,400
His Majesty is using the people
of Yueluo to intimidate Sanlang,

551
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:32,770
making it hard for him to speak.

552
00:40:33,192 --> 00:40:34,856
Order the Changfeng Guards
to be vigilant.

553
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:35,670
Make sure

554
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:37,080
the people are protected.

